FW Laptop accessories Cc Bill Are you the original owner of that laptop or is it a redeployed sysem Also what model Original Message From Wendt Richard Sent Wednesday November AM To LaGesse Denise Subject RE Laptop accessories Not knowing exactly what model Compaq laptop Bill has makes this an educated guess on my part First of all all new laptops came with both CD and floppy drives so if he is the orginal owner have him check in the bag If it was a redeployed system he may not have received all the pieces With that said an internal floppy drive will run about for the Compaq M laptop Other models may vary in price a bit but probably not by much Original Message From LaGesse Denise Sent Tuesday November PM To Wendt Richard Subject FW Laptop accessories Im sending this to you in Karons absence Original Message From LaGesse Denise Sent Tuesday November PM To OGorman Karon Cc Rapp Bill Sellers Emily Subject Laptop accessories Bill Rapps laptop Compaq is not equipped with the device that allows a diskette to be loaded He can run CDs but not diskettes What do we need to order and how much will it cost Thanks Denise LaGesse Enron Transportation Services Smith Street PO Box Houston Texas ph cell fax

Color Laser PrinterThe Color Laser Printer in my cube is up and running now For those of you who had previously added this color printer to your selections youll need to delete that old icon because its totally different this time Heres how you delete it Start in the lower lefthand corner of your monitor Settings Printers Highlight the printer you want to delete call me if youre unsure which one Press the delete button on your keyboard Make sure thats the one you really want to delete and click YES Heres how you gain access to the new one Start Run In the box that says Open type in the following without the underlining wnahouHPColorL OK YES This printer has now been added to your printer selections Lee You dont have to do anything because I already added it to your computer PLEASE NOTE If youre printing to LEGAL paper youll need to manually change the paper cartridge before you select print If you call me Id be happy to change the cartridge to LEGAL for you but I ask that you change it back to LETTER once you print so that its not an inconvenience to others Mucho thanks Call me if questions Thanks for you patience in getting this up and running again Denise LaGesse Enron Transportation Services Smith Street PO Box Houston Texas ph fax

RE Color Laser PrinterBy the way it prints on legalsize paper but only in blackwhitegray not in color Original Message From LaGesse Denise Sent Thursday October AM To Rapp Bill Bargainer David K Brown William E Cobden Jan Cones Janet Crowley Philip Fossum Drew Holtzman Staci Huber Lee King Jr Frazier Kyle Candace Mann Ruth McCoppin Dorothy Melton Richard Pryor Tony Raker Colleen Sellers Emily Smith Maxine Soldano Louis Waser Iris Wilkie Kim Subject Color Laser Printer The Color Laser Printer in my cube is up and running now For those of you who had previously added this color printer to your selections youll need to delete that old icon because its totally different this time Heres how you delete it Start in the lower lefthand corner of your monitor Settings Printers Highlight the printer you want to delete call me if youre unsure which one Press the delete button on your keyboard Make sure thats the one you really want to delete and click YES Heres how you gain access to the new one Start Run In the box that says Open type in the following without the underlining wnahouHPColorL OK YES This printer has now been added to your printer selections Lee You dont have to do anything because I already added it to your computer PLEASE NOTE If youre printing to LEGAL paper youll need to manually change the paper cartridge before you select print If you call me Id be happy to change the cartridge to LEGAL for you but I ask that you change it back to LETTER once you print so that its not an inconvenience to others Mucho thanks Call me if questions Thanks for you patience in getting this up and running again Denise LaGesse Enron Transportation Services Smith Street PO Box Houston Texas ph fax
